title: 599. Breaking Down Le'Veon Bell's Release + Rodgers vs. Brady Preview
itunes:title: 599. Breaking Down Le'Veon Bell's Release + Rodgers vs. Brady Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys react to running back Le'Veon Bell's release from the Jets, while focusing on why the Jets made this move (:53). Then, the pair preview Sunday's matchup between Packers QB Aaron Rodgers and Bucs QB Tom Brady (20:31). To wrap up the show, the duo talk about Bucky's alma mater North Carolina and also Isaiah Simmons' fit with the Arizona Cardinals (29:11).
